0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-chriistopher-polk-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-chriistopher-polk-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-chriistopher-polk-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>表示，巡演时她有时会一次睡 13 个小时，因为太累了。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/olivia-rodrigo-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3756151">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 伦敦现场演出：很可能是 2024 年最有趣的巡演</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位艺术家刚刚结束了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-2024-guts-world-tour-shows-buy-tickets-3497458">大型“GUTS”世界巡演</a>，最近接受了<a href="https://www.complex.com/music/a/eric-skelton/olivia-rodrigo-interview-guts-popup-la" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Complex 的</em></a>采访，谈论了她在路上的生活。</p><p> “嗯，巡演时我睡了很多觉。我有时一天睡13个小时。我太累了，”她告诉媒体。 “所以很多时间都这样过去了。但我刚刚在读书，也一直在观看我所有的安慰节目。我每天都会看<em>《欲望都市》，</em>让自己感觉自己脚踏实地、宾至如归。”</p><p>罗德里戈住在洛杉矶，当她在起亚论坛上表演时，她可以回家睡在自己的床上。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784668" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784668" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784668" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-christopher-polk.jpg" alt="奥利维亚罗德里戈" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-christopher-polk.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-christopher-polk-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-christopher-polk-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-christopher-polk-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/olivia-rodrigo-christopher-polk-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uplo